      <section id="id1171953243049">
        <title>To answer questions on map work [LO 1.5]</title>
        <para id="id8704300">Look carefully at the map key of South Africa and answer the following questions:</para>
        <para id="id1171954211836">1. Which big mountain range do we find in Kwazulu-Natal?  </para>
        <para id="id4022477">2. Name three minerals that are mined in the Northern Cape. </para>
        <para id="id2214240"/>
        <para id="id7374521">3. Which province is the farthest north? </para>
        <para id="id2023868">4. Which river on the northern border of the Northern Cape flows into the Atlantic Ocean?</para>
        <para id="id1171964070613"/>
        <para id="id1171953988988">5. In which ocean will you be swimming when holidaying in Durban?  </para>
        <para id="id8334927">6. Which province is the smallest? </para>
        <para id="id8214833">7. In which province are you when you are on a holiday in Port Elizabeth? </para>
        <para id="id6809447"/>
        <list id="id1171957618333" list-type="enumerated" number-style="arabic">
          <item>True / False? The coal mined in Mpumalanga can be exported to other countries by boat</item>
        </list>
