      <section id="id1171957407034">
        <title>To use information from sources to answer questions about people and places [LO 1.5]</title>
        <para id="id8267008">Your educator will hang a wall map of the world in the classroom. Listen to the world news every day and read newspapers. Bring geography articles to class and let your educator indicate with a pin on the wall map on which continent the events occurred. Discuss them and give your own opinion.</para>
        <para id="id7999219">TRY TO CONTINUE WITH THIS ASSIGNMENT UNTIL THE END OF THE YEAR.</para>
        <para id="id3670536"/>
